response.overview: Fiodor is an insecure young gay man who agrees to hookup through an app with Simón. When the moment arrives, Fiodor’s discomfort and fears manifest as letters emerging from his body. Together with Simón, they will try to arrange the letters to make sense of the situation.
response.tagline: Beware the Jabberwock, my son! The jaws that bite, the claws that catch!
response.title: Jabberwockies
